'body': 'MSFT employees can try out our new experience at [OpenAPI Hub](https://aka.ms/openapiportal) - one location for using our validation tools and finding your workflow. In this PR, we are adding support for the new API version 2021-10-15-preview. All of the changes in this PR were already approved in a previous PR to the private repo. These PRs are: 1. https://github.com/Azure/azure-rest-api-specs-pr/pull/4666 2. https://github.com/Azure/azure-rest-api-specs-pr/pull/5567 3. https://github.com/Azure/azure-rest-api-specs-pr/pull/6074 4. https://github.com/Azure/azure-rest-api-specs-pr/pull/6488 The changes in this PR includes, but is not limited to: 1. Add Event Subscriptions as a nested resource under Domains, Topics, and Domain Topics 2. Partner related changes including partner configuration, verified partners, partner destinations and channels 3. Geopair changes 4. Management Group changes 5. Others ### Changelog Add a changelog entry for this PR by answering the following questions: 1. In this PR, we are adding support for the new API version 2021-10-15-preview. All of the changes in this PR were already approved in a previous PR to the private repo. These PRs are: 

1. https://github.com/Azure/azure-rest-api-specs-pr/pull/4666
2. https://github.com/Azure/azure-rest-api-specs-pr/pull/5567
3. https://github.com/Azure/azure-rest-api-specs-pr/pull/6074
4. https://github.com/Azure/azure-rest-api-specs-pr/pull/6488

The changes in this PR includes, but is not limited to:
1. Add Event Subscriptions as a nested resource under Domains, Topics, and Domain Topics
2. Partner related changes including partner configuration, verified partners, partner destinations and channels
3. Geopair changes
4. Management Group changes
5. Others
